entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You are working to discover the identity of the leaders of the Chirq Council.
entries.journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the Chirq Council by earning the trust of one of the underbosses. Use that trust to find the leaders of the Chirq Council.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Chirq Council: Moving Up - Part One
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go speak with Jzoro Quanera, a Chirq Council underboss. It was to Jzoro that Kazic had reported.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Jzoro wants you to oversee the handling of a shipment of spice that is being delivered to the area. Your true mission will be to take the spice and switch it with a fake. Be sure to get rid of all witnesses at the delivery site.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go to Cpatain Baize to switch out the crates of spice with fake ones. The fake crates contain a small amount of spice cut with a common medicinal powder.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Go to Captain Baize to Switch the Spice
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Take the fake spice to Jzoro.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Jzoro has heard rumors that a small-time thug operating in Doaba Guerfel is actually an undercover CorSec agent. He doesn't care if it's true or not, but he wants that person eliminated. You know that he must be talking about Lilith Laughlin. Go warn her.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: To keep Lilith safe, you are going to convince Jzoro that a terrorist leader named Ebela Puckett is the undercover CorSec agent. Ebela Puckett is the leader of the Grey Shroud terrorists.
entries.task07_item_name: You have used the CorSec terminal to make a CorSec ID
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Use the picture you took of Ebela Puckett and the CorSec terminal next to Captain Baize to manufacture a fake CorSec ID for Ebela Puckett. Captain Baize has authorized your access to the terminal.
entries.task10_item_name: You have taken a picture of Ebela Puckett
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: You'll need to take Ebela's picture. [To take her picture, select Ebela Puckett as your intended target, and then double-click the camera in your inventory.]
entries.task12_item_name: You have taken a crate of spice
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Monumenter poachers who are deliverying the spice.
entries.task14_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Chirq Council ruffians that were sent to the spice delivery site as your protection.
